{"tid":931705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳公立名校新規： 住所小於500呎限入學","createTime":"2018-12-07T08:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T12:49:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e60c62989eaab723c7f5205bc56c665a35e383a6","tid":931705,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181207/20563076\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181207%2F20563076&d=OaCoICW24oY6%2FNaEHQbAyMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=48bd2ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181207%2F20563076&h=e07abd58\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181207/20563076</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月07日 <br />\n<br />\n深圳公立名校新規：<br />\n住所小於500呎限入學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181207/large/a2104a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181207%2Flarge%2Fa2104a.gif&h=6c1825d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳市螺嶺外國語實驗學校（圖）日前發公告，下年起住所50平方米（約538平方呎）下的學童將被限制入學。公告稱這是為優先保障學校地段內，適齡兒童入學權利。輿論炮轟，有律師直指對低收入家庭不公、侵犯學生平等教育權且違憲，校方隨後撤去公告。<br />\n<br />\n有關公告顯示，明年起對申請該校學生，家住的面積小於或等於30平方米（322平方呎）的，需購房及實際居住滿六年以上。大於30平方米且小於或等於50平方米，需購房及實際居住滿四年，大於50平方米以上不受限制。北京京師律師事務所雷國亞律師指，該校做法是對低收入家庭設限，侵犯孩子的平等受教育權。這種教育資源分配與公民財產數量掛鈎不公平，與憲法精神不符。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後惹爭議，羅湖區教育部門介入。該校官網昨撤去公告。資料顯示，該小學為深圳公立名校，廣東省一級學校，為羅湖區教育改革試點單位，學校佔地逾3萬平方米，有60個教學班，在校學生近3,000人，有教職工168人。 　<br />\n《北京青年報》  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n與男友上電視爆紅　清華校花約3P被拒爆粗"},{"pid":"40f0f25308b6faeb38f75db3235aca7f169c59c1","tid":931705,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:30:07.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca97acc28f873ca355d02dda27f922a2ce25af4d","tid":931705,"uid":85116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:31:13.000Z","msg":"與男友上電視爆紅　清華校花約3P被拒爆粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a13f493b8fca86012ff6eca2ee8917218342c48","tid":931705,"uid":22422,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:32:30.000Z","msg":"為咗救支那地產股<br />\n共匪可以玩到幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e7f7ecb889735a5cc67d021d1fa69713cee0df","tid":931705,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca97acc28f873ca355d02dda27f922a2ce25af4d","tid":931705,"uid":85116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:31:13.000Z","msg":"與男友上電視爆紅　清華校花約3P被拒爆粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"樓主平時睇開呢d新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b109e9707361001278b5b9fa7a64c312e46f08a1","tid":931705,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca97acc28f873ca355d02dda27f922a2ce25af4d","tid":931705,"uid":85116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:31:13.000Z","msg":"與男友上電視爆紅　清華校花約3P被拒爆粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T08:34:11.000Z","msg":"唔好search黎睇, 岩岩入左去睇好樣衰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cb40cb566ad8a7493368c52c9c1fe37aa6476a","tid":931705,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"社會主義（資本主義）萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/